reviewText: I am the biggest D.L. Hughley fan and anything he is in, I'll buy. This has a lot of great comedians and crazy funny.
This is a very funny man. A great show, one of his best!
Really funny!!!  I enjoyed laughing at this!! Laughter is the best medicine and this is a healthy dose!!!  Watch this and get ready to laugh out loud!!  This is Very Funny!!
A little disappointed, thought it would be better with some of the names on here. It was ok, some very parts but also some dead parts too.
DL does a pretty good job as host and the line-up of comedians is satisfactory. This is probably worth watching, but it won't split your sides too often.
